    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >s&amp;box is a game creation platform built on the Source 2 engine and our spiritual successor to Garry's Mod.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play, create, and share games, explore community creations, and experience endless sandbox fun with powerful modern tools.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY GAMES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >s&amp;box is full of games created by the community of every genre. Party up and play with your friends.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREATE GAMES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anyone can create games using our intuitive modern editor, creating scenes with a standard scene system and a C# API with powerful hotloading.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY FUND</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can publish your games directly to the platform where everyone can play it at the click of a button.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can earn through our <strong>Play Fund</strong> from players playing your games, directly funded from cosmetic purchases.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPORT GAMES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or if you want, you can publish your games to Steam, royalty-free. (<i>although we're not quite ready on this yet</i>)</p>",
